=== MGF4R
 
- Code on GitHub [http://github.com/mcommons/mgf4r]
 
=== Description
 
Ruby client for Mobile Giving Foundation API. Used by Mobile Commons for processing mobile donations over SMS [http://mcommons.com/mobile-fundraising].

Based on the API described at http://services.mobilegiving.org/Service.asmx


=== Authors

- Maintained by [Benjamin Stein](mailto:ben@mcommons.com), [Mal McKay](mailto:mal@mcommons.com) & [Nathan Woodhull](mailto:nathan@mcommons.com)

